Emily Ann Lloyd https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emily_Ann_Lloyd 0 Emily Ann Lloyd (born Emily Ann Morelli; March 27, 1984) is an American actress. She is best known for her role as Susan Lovell, the daughter of Jim Lovell, in Apollo 13. Emily_Ann_Lloyd ( born Emily_Ann_Morelli ; March_27_,_1984 ) is an_American_actress .
